<plot>Awakening is about the social and economic empowerment of severely marginalized women in Afghanistan and India. As these women courageously band together to transcend their historically restricted roles, a new ethos is spreading. An emerging economic system with values like sharing, mutuality, collaboration and closeness to nature emerges as a counter-text to Globalism and points to a way that could eradicate severe poverty in our lifetime.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?052890</url></doc>
